Credit to The Original Peanut <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/scp-173">SCP-173</a>, for being a notable article and a prime.<br />
Credit to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/weryllium" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2727655); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2727655&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1583730051" alt="Weryllium" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2727655)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/weryllium" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2727655); return false;">Weryllium</a></span> for <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/scp-4597">SCP-4597</a>. Another convenient prime and a decent anomaly to expose Andrew to.<br />
Credit to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/salman-corbette" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(678987); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=678987&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1583730051" alt="Salman Corbette" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=678987)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/salman-corbette" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(678987); return false;">Salman Corbette</a></span> for the <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/recording-stuff-or-whatever">funny orientation</a><br />
